      "content": "hey so im working on this new streetwear line for my brand and i really dont want it to feel like we're just some corporate company doing cultural appropriation lol. i want it to feel real. can u help me define what the actual \"authentic\" urban aesthetic is right now? like what are the core elements that make something feel truly street and not just fake?",
